sub_title: Senior policy advisor research policy, Faculty of Science, Utrecht University
summary: I am an enthusiastic and practical-minded policy officer with a background in biology. I am strong in coordinating and managing a variety of tasks and can transition well from strategic to operational thinking. I am used to dealing with administrative processes and their sensitivities and have extensive experience with scientific policy advice. My communication skills are excellent. I enjoy writing and have a great sense of responsibility.
